function ursAppDocEvent() {
    document.getElementById("form_appUploadDetails").addEventListener("submit",
            function(event) {
                event.preventDefault();
                
                var fileSelect = document.getElementById('fileUploaderDijit');
                var uploadButton = document.getElementById('submitAppDocButton');
                var uploadDocType = dijit.byId('appDocType').get('value');

                if(typeof uploadDocType == "undefined"
					 || uploadDocType == null || uploadDocType == "__NONE__" || uploadDocType == "NONE" || uploadDocType.length == 0){
                	globalUrsRegWizardController.showMessage('Please select the Document Type');
                	return false;
                }
                
             // Get the selected files from the input.
                var files = fileSelect.files;
             //var files = dijit.byId("fileUploaderDijit").getFileList();
                if(files && files.length > 0) {
	             // Create a new FormData object.
	                var formData = new FormData();
	                formData.append('appDocType', uploadDocType);
	                formData.append('applicantId', globalUrsRegWizardController.getWizardControllerMap().applicantId);
	                formData.append('filingTypeId', globalUrsRegWizardController.getWizardControllerMap().filingTypeId);
	                
	             // Loop through each of the selected files.
	                for (var i = 0; i < files.length; i++) {
	                  var file = files[i];
	
	                  // Check the file type.
	                  if (!file.type.match('pdf.*')) {
	                	  globalUrsRegWizardController.showMessage("You can upload only PDF Documents");
	                	  return false;
	                    	//continue;
	                  }
	
	                  // Add the file to the request.
	                  formData.append('appDocuments[]', file, file.name);
	                }
	                uploadButton.innerHTML = 'Uploading...';
	                callServletInfo(formData, uploadButton);                                                      
	            } else {
	            	globalUrsRegWizardController.showMessage("No file was selected.  Select a file and try again.");
	            }
            }, false);
}

function callServletInfo(formData, uploadButton){
	
	// Set up the request.
    var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
 
 // Open the connection.
    xhr.open('POST', '/UrsRegistrationWizard/UploadDocsServlet', true);
 
 // Set up a handler for when the request finishes.
    xhr.onload = function () {
      if (xhr.status === 200) {
        // File(s) uploaded. currently going with status 200 -- but if we need to verify the wm response then enable this code
        //if (xhr.status === 200 && xhr.responseText == 'true') {

        globalUrsRegWizardController.refreshAppDocGrid();
        uploadButton.innerHTML = 'Upload';
      } else {
        uploadButton.innerHTML = 'Upload';
//        alert('An error occurred! Please contact system Administration\n'+xhr.responseText);
        var exObj = JSON.parse(xhr.responseText);
        globalUrsRegWizardController.handleSpecialError(exObj.errorMessage, exObj);
      }
    };
    
 // Send the Data.
    xhr.send(formData);
}

function ursAppDocEvent() {
    document.getElementById("form_appUploadDetails").addEventListener("submit",
            function(event) {
                event.preventDefault();
                
                var fileSelect = document.getElementById('fileUploaderDijit');
                var uploadButton = document.getElementById('submitAppDocButton');
                var uploadDocType = dijit.byId('appDocType').get('value');

                if(typeof uploadDocType == "undefined"
					 || uploadDocType == null || uploadDocType == "__NONE__" || uploadDocType == "NONE" || uploadDocType.length == 0){
                	globalUrsRegWizardController.showMessage('Please select the Document Type');
                	return false;
                }
                
             // Get the selected files from the input.
                var files = fileSelect.files;
             //var files = dijit.byId("fileUploaderDijit").getFileList();
                if(files && files.length > 0) {
	             // Create a new FormData object.
	                var formData = new FormData();
	                formData.append('appDocType', uploadDocType);
	                formData.append('applicantId', globalUrsRegWizardController.getWizardControllerMap().applicantId);
	                formData.append('filingTypeId', globalUrsRegWizardController.getWizardControllerMap().filingTypeId);
	                
	             // Loop through each of the selected files.
	                for (var i = 0; i < files.length; i++) {
	                  var file = files[i];
	
	                  // Check the file type.
	                  if (!file.type.match('pdf.*')) {
	                	  globalUrsRegWizardController.showMessage("You can upload only PDF Documents");
	                	  return false;
	                    	//continue;
	                  }
	
	                  // Add the file to the request.
	                  formData.append('appDocuments[]', file, file.name);
	                }
	                uploadButton.innerHTML = 'Uploading...';
	                callServletInfo(formData, uploadButton);                                                      
	            } else {
	            	globalUrsRegWizardController.showMessage("No file was selected.  Select a file and try again.");
	            }
            }, false);
}

function callServletInfo(formData, uploadButton){
	
	// Set up the request.
    var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
 
 // Open the connection.
    xhr.open('POST', '/UrsRegistrationWizard/UploadDocsServlet', true);
 
 // Set up a handler for when the request finishes.
    xhr.onload = function () {
      if (xhr.status === 200) {
        // File(s) uploaded. currently going with status 200 -- but if we need to verify the wm response then enable this code
        //if (xhr.status === 200 && xhr.responseText == 'true') {

        globalUrsRegWizardController.refreshAppDocGrid();
        uploadButton.innerHTML = 'Upload';
      } else {
        uploadButton.innerHTML = 'Upload';
//        alert('An error occurred! Please contact system Administration\n'+xhr.responseText);
        var exObj = JSON.parse(xhr.responseText);
        globalUrsRegWizardController.handleSpecialError(exObj.errorMessage, exObj);
      }
    };
    
 // Send the Data.
    xhr.send(formData);
}

         case 'exitUrs':
             globalUrsRegWizardController.exitRegistration();

             globalUrsRegWizardController.viewReport();
